intp (0.1.0-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging skeleton (Stage 1.5 of upstream roadmap).
  * Source-only — no binary release yet; the upstream code base is
    still scaffolding and the binaries do not yet implement the
    seven core metrics.
  * The packaging shape (intp, libintp1, libintp-dev, intp-doc,
    intp-plugin-bpftrace) is validated by CI's lintian gate so that
    once Stage 2 of the roadmap lands, the move to a personal PPA
    (Stage 4) is mechanical.

